profile:
Weed Man has been providing lawn care since 1970. Weed Man Sarnia has grown within the community along with our customers. Over the past decade lawn care has gone through tremendous changes. We have embraced these changes and perfected new approaches allowing us to continue delivering the valuable lawn care service our Sarnia Lambton clients have come to expect.

We have been a presence in the community providing superior lawn care services that include things such as weed management, insect management, fertilization, core aeration, seed & feed and much more. We provide our clients with personal service which is crucial for the growth and maintenance of a beautiful, lush, green and healthy lawn.Â 

Our hometown, Sarnia, boasts spectacular white beaches and brilliant evening sunsets on the shores of Lake Huron. Sarnia is the birthplace of Canadian Astronaut Chris Hadfield & PGA Tour Golf Professional Mike Weir as well as home to the Sarnia Sting Junior A Hockey Team. The Judith & Norman Alix Art Gallery has an impressive collection, which includes 35 pieces from the Group of Seven.
